PACKAGE INFO
Textmate Bundle for OpenErp XML files
Snippets are meant to be used with Openerp 5 or later

OpenerpXML allows you to easily create Openerp XML Data files and fill them by useful snippets for records, views, workflows, etc.

INSTALLATION
Just copy this directory into your ~/Library/Application\ Support/TextMate/Bundles/ directory, and reload bundles. That's it!

You'll have a new bundle named XML Openerp among yours!
